    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Venture burrows underground with Drill Dash to bypass barriers and chokepoints entirely, surfacing behind the enemy line to detonate Smart Excavator charges at close range.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Burrowing telegraphs their general direction and they have no ranged option once they surface, so a team that tracks the burrow and focuses them on emergence punishes the dive hard.</p>"
